content: I want to wake up at 7:30 am, which is my usual time. I'd like to start exercising at 7:45 am and meditating at 8:15 am. I'd like to commit to this routine 5 days a week, from Monday to Friday. I prefer to receive notifications on my phone, and I'd like to receive one reminder 30 minutes before waking up and another 15 minutes before.
